CloudWatch to deliver metrics.

119
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:59,943
So I like to use CloudWatch dashboards,

120
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:04,530
kind of I compare it to an
actual dashboard like on my car.

121
00:05:04,530 --> 00:05:06,780
