00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:10,980
I'm looking at the fuel level

124
00:05:10,980 --> 00:05:13,380
because I'm getting like five
miles per gallon on my car,

125
00:05:13,380 --> 00:05:15,990
and I'm also looking at the
transmission temperature.

126
00:05:15,990 --> 00:05:16,980
So if there's an issue,

127
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:18,540
'cause I don't normally
pull a camper every day,

128
00:05:18,540 --> 00:05:20,460
I know exactly what to look at.

129
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:21,540
I know if it gets too hot,

